profile: We have been in the snow removal business for the past 5 years and have been able to consistently provide a consistant, fast and reliable service every year.  We make sure to keep our main focus being customer service and keeping everyone we work with as happy as possible in order to create a personal connection.  Stay warm this winter and choose the Peterborough Snowmen as your snow removal partner.
